<s> Hi, In reading though the HTTP/1.0 memo with info header HTTP Working Group T. Berners-Lee, MIT/LCS INTERNET-DRAFT R. Fielding, UC Irvine draft-ietf-http-v10-spec-05.html H. Frystyk, MIT/LCS Expires August 19, 1996 February 19, 1996 I'm a bit confused by section 3.2.2 http URL.  </s>
<s> Based on the general syntax presented in section 3.2.1, an http URL can include 'params'.  </s>
